org.eclipse.rdf4j.queryrender.builder

Interface QueryBuilder<T extends ParsedQuery>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SupportsGroups
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractQueryBuilder
    Deprecated. 
    use SparqlBuilder instead.

    @Deprecated
public interface QueryBuilder<T extends ParsedQuery>
extends SupportsGroups

    Interface for a QueryBuilder which provides a simple fluent API for constructing Sesame query object programmatically.

    Author:
    Michael Grove
